author: Carmen Cox
title: Kasey Kahne's a New Dad
text:
Share Article 
Jeff Zelevansky/NASCAR via Getty Images (NEW YORK) — Kasey Kahne and his longtime girlfriend, Sam Sheets, have welcomed their first child.The Hendrick Motorsports driver announced the good news Tuesday morning on Twitter. "I officially became a dad at 1:11 AM to Tanner Lee Kahne. Mom and [T]anner are doing great. On no sleep but we can't put this little guy down," he wrote .Kahne, 35, reveled to ESPN in June that Sheets was pregnant.Kahne is currently 18th in the Sprint Cup Series standings.Copyright © 2015, ABC Radio.
